data.description: Welcome to Old Mandarin and this large multi-generational 5 bed, 3 bath home!  There is no HOA and it sits back on a quiet culdesac with a private vinyl fenced backyard.  2-car side garage with workshop, aluminum RV carport, concrete and vinyl siding,120mph high impact windows, 2017 Architectural roof, paver patios-front and back, wood- burning fireplace with cathedral ceiling and atrium in family room, gas fireplace in additional family room. Murphy Bed included in one bedroom.  Two AC's, two fireplaces, 2 laundry rooms.  This is a must-see home! Well for irrigation, gas line for future outdoor kitchen and room for a pool. This owner has set you up for your own personal touches! (Extra flooring for home stored in garage)
